snippet.title: Caromble! skill level gameplay: The Race
snippet.description:
This is Caromble! A fresh new take on the brick break game!

Now on Steam Early Access!

In this video we show one run of our skill level: The Race. This level was a dream of Peter for quite some years now, but finally it is finished. And we love it! That ending where you need to charge is crazy.

Steam: store.steampowered.com/app/347660
Game info: www.caromble.com
